# Solo App 3 — Fetch & Display Data

## API Used
- Dog CEO API
- Endpoint: `https://dog.ceo/api/breeds/image/random`

## How to Run
Ensure Flutter SDK is installed
- Add dependency in `pubspec.yaml`:
  dependencies:
    http: ^1.2.2
Run commands:
flutter pub get
flutter run

## User Actions
Fetch Another Dog → loads a new random dog image
Retry (error state) → retries the request

## Features
HTTP GET request to public API
JSON parsing with dart:convert
Loading spinner during fetch
Error message + retry button on failure
Displays dog image with styling & padding
Empty-state fallback

## Edge Case
No internet / bad URL → shows error UI with retry option
